After a temporary spell in which Oliver Queen was dead and his son had taken over the mantle of Green Arrow, writer and director Kevin Smith brought him back to kick off this terrific series that re-introduced the Emerald Archer back into the DC Universe proper - where he always belonged. This run was immensely popular and featured some great writing and art. Judd Winnick also had a long spell at the helm of this title, and it would all lead into the eventual marriage of GA and Black Canary (in an entirely separate run). These brand new DIGITAL copies of the whole volume are presented thanks to Empire; huge thanks to them for their (usual) great work. Please seed and enjoy! :-)
